      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been preserved in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless finish and an interior devoid of wear. Meticulously maintained and mechanically superior, it represents a rare acquisition for those who demand uncompromising quality. Every detail reflects a standard of care that transcends the typical market offering.",
