    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and kept in a garage, so it\u2019s sparkling inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
