      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you won\u2019t find another one like this. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered since day one. It looks and drives just like it did when it first rolled off the lot\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is definitely the one. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
