      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a perfectly calibrated M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing sharp, adaptive response. Comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been performed to ensure peak engine longevity. The exterior and interior are in concours condition, devoid of typical bolster wear or rock chips, representing a rare opportunity to own a preserved analog icon.",
